description:
May 3, 2018 / Rebecca Lavoie hosts this addendum with Susan, Colin, and Madeleine Baran, for a discussion on Episode 2 of the Pam Lanier case, updates in the Joey Watkins case, and the recently released Season 2 of Madeleine's podcast "In the Dark," on the Curtis Flowers case in Winona, Mississippi.&#13;
&#13;
Episode scoring music by Animal Weapon and Blue Dot Sessions.&#13;
&#13;
